OL,4,CMoffat schoolboy wears skirt in protest
OL,5,Cat dress code
OL,6, A teenage boy has been wearing a skirt
OL,7, to school in protest after some pupils
OL,8, were sent home for wearing shorts in
OL,9, warm weather.
OL,11,FMoffat Academy's uniform policy says
OL,12,Fstudents should only wear either dark
OL,13,Ftrousers or a skirt.
OL,15,FShane Richardson, 16, borrowed a skirt
OL,16,Ffrom his younger sister Lexi to join
OL,17,Fthe protest.
OL,19,FDumfries and Galloway Council said the
OL,20,Funiform policy had been in place for
OL,21,Fsome time but was due to be changed.
